name: FingerPunk #023 (Zombie Zed)
description: Zed looks scary but he is actually one of the most friendly FingerPunks. He once ventured out to the edge of the metaverse, the rumor is he fell into a memory hole and came out with a certain "condition". Some FingerPunks avoid him now due to the fear his "condition" could be contagious.
